  "texts": [
    "This preference was reflected in the DDSPbased speech synthesis literature we reviewed, in which every paper conducted a listening test.",
    "Conversely, only slightly over half of the work reviewed on music and singing voice synthesis conducted a subjective evaluation of results.",
    "This discrepancy may be partially explained by the existence of standards for subjective evaluation in speech research, in contrast to music.",
    "That being said, it became clear through this review that there exists no single unified method for evaluating DDSP synthesis results.",
    "In the following subsections we detail the more widely used evaluation methods, and discuss how these have been used in work to date."
